\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 No, they haven't got one now. And we used to have - bring stamps, and every Easter we used to give them all Easter eggs.
