\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Chocolate ones. Yes. And then we used to take them for a ride once a ye}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12322035\charrsid7682985 ar
}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985  in a coach, all of us used to g
o off. And when I was in the choir down there, Dad and me, used to go for a Choir outing, we used to get up at 5 o'clock in the morning, walk to Pewsey, catch a train, go to Bournemouth and have a nice day down there, and come back to Pewsey at night and 
walk home from Pewsey, get home about }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12322035\charrsid7682985 11}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985  o'clock at night. That was our day out.
