 arm and he couldn't shave and that. He was sexton at the Church for }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12322035\charrsid7682985 16}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985  or }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
