\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 , all her grand clothes to wear.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 And did she have to learn her lines by heard.
