Oh, she used to do wonderful! My wife was good, she could spell anything, she could read anything, she could write anything, more than whatever I could.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Did she also go to the school here?
