No, she went to Marlborough School. She were born at Surbiton, and her father died a week before she were born. Well then, her mother brought he}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2819877\charrsid7682985 r}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985  to Marlborough and lived with her grandmother, grandmother brought May up, and her mother went back to London - cook-housekeeper.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 And she stayed down in this part?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Yes, Marlborough. And she thought more of her }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12322035\charrsid7682985 Granny}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985  than she did of her mother. Her mother got cross over that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Did she ever go and visit her mother? After her mother went back as a cook-housekeeper?
