\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 I met her down in Wilcot Manor. Used to go there with the bread.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 I see, and she was working there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Yes. She was one of the housemaids. There were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2819877\charrsid7682985 10}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985  there then. Butler lady's maid.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 How old were you when you met her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Nineteen, something like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 And she, was she younger?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Ah, she was older'n me, five years. She were 80 when she died.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Did you start walking out with her quite soon after you met her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Yes. We were engaged }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2819877\charrsid7682985 5}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985  years. She u}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2819877\charrsid7682985 sed to come up home to Granny\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 , and then I used to go into Marlborough.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Did you know her quite a long time before you decided to ask her to get married to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Oh, yes. And then when we did get m
arried, we were going to be married at Wilcot, had the Banns published, couldn't get home from the war and then I come home all of a sudden and then we was married in London with a Special Licence. Her mother came up and give her away and my cousin came, 
best man and then we had - we went to Wimbledon, we had some friends, and had meal, and then we come back to Marlborough for our honeymoon.
