\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 And when you came back in 1916 were just the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2819877\charrsid7682985 2}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985  of you living here, or did you have any other relatives?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 No, only us }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2819877\charrsid7682985 2}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
