\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 No, she didn't do anything. Never had her work from the day I married her until she died.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Was she glad of that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Hm, I didn't want her to go out to work. 'Course, weren't much money 'til after I left Mr. Hales'}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2819877\charrsid7682985 .}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985  I went to Pewsey Hospital to work. I was there 18 years.
