\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 They give me this chair.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 It's a good chair isn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Oh, lovely one, yes. Give me that as a present.
