\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 \'a3}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 10 a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 That was very good money, wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Yes, and then I had a pension when I left, and I was there 18 }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2819877\charrsid7682985 
