\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 I had a nice book, a college boy's book,}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2194781\charrsid7682985  \lquote Julian Holme\rquote }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 .
