}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 \'a3}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 8 when Grandmother were buried. Now what, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
