\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Yes, come round. B}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9306789\charrsid7682985 ut we didn't pay much, not 'til we got on and got a bit 
}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 more money, then we paid more.
