he wrote, and that. And that's May with the fowls. That's when we got married, and that's me the hospital.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Can I read this aloud?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Thank you very much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 "The Army Service Corps, May Woodger Milton, July 26}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \super\insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 th}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 , 1915." That would before you were married.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7682985\charrsid7682985 <p}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 oem>"Not brought before the public eye
\par in a very marked degree,
\par Yes valiant and brave for their country
\par Are the men of the A.S.C.
\par "Never seen in the trenches,
\par Yet from danger they would not flee
\par If an act of theirs could save our flag,
\par Brave men of the A.S.C.
\par "Our brave men would faint with hunger,
\par The enemy victorious be,
\par Were it not for a few of their comrades,
\par The men of the A.S.C.
\par "No regiments more worthy of honour
\par Though they serve in a humbler degree
\par Than the ones who feed the Army,
\par The men of the A.S.C.
\par "And when again in peaceful days
\par Flies the flag of liberty,
\par May the deeds ne'er be forgotten
\par Which are done by the A.S.C.
\par {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname date}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Month}{\xmlattrvalue 7}}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Day}{\xmlattrvalue 26}}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Year}{\xmlattrvalue 1915}}}July, 26}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\super\insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 th}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 , 1915{\*\xmlclose}."</}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12679746 p}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 oem>
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 She wrote that, that shows she could write things.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Yes, she could, couldn't she. And she got money for it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Not for that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Not for that one. She just sent that in, did she, and they published it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Was it a competition, or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 That was before you went to the War, because you went in 1917, didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 1915.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 1915, but afterwards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Can you remember when she wrote this one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 No, I don't.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7682985\charrsid7682985 <p}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 oem>"ABSENT ONES
\par "To absent ones our thoughts go out
\par Wherever we may be.
\par Not a day goes by without
\par Some tender memory.
\par "Whatever our steps may lead
\par Or what our lips may say,
\par The heart remembers, keeping faith
\par With loved ones far away.
\par "And sometimes in the busy hours,
\par Or in a crowded place
\par There comes a fleeting vision
\par Of a dear, remembered face.
\par "A passing word may strike a chord
\par On memory's golden strings,
\par And wake the echoing music -
\par The unforgotten things."</}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12679746 p}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 oem>
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Written in the War, do you think, or later?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 No, in the War, when I was away.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Thank you for letting me see those, they're lovely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 That's my friend, when he got married. He's been married 28 years now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 And you were the best man, were you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Ah, see me there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 I'm not sure which is you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 That's me, the outside one. That's my wife with the fowls, when we had the fowls. And that was us when we got married.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Oh, that's a lovely photograph, isn't it. You look fine in uniform.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 See the different clothes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Did she get a special outfit for the wedding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 No, t'was just a costume.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Very nice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Hm, that's another one, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Were you in the A.S.C.?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 At first, and then I was transferred into the King's Royal Rifles. I went out as a baker, you see.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Oh, I see, yes. To France?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Hm. And then we went to the Dardanelles, you see, and then I was put in the King's Royal Rifles.
