{\*\xmlclose}, when we were there, every time would go down in the town, she used to give us half a crown to spend. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16333885\charrsid7682985 Every}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 
 one of us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Was that her own money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Yes, her own money, she had plenty of money. Oh, yes. Oh, and didn't we live well! Tremendous big rice puddings, right big 'uns.
