naughty }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 I'll call a policeman.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 They never said that to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 You weren't a very naughty little boy though were you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 No 'cos - sometimes I was - I had to go to bed once, dad was - dad w
as very strict and we done anything wrong had to go to bed without any - tea. But after we'd gone if dad had gone out grandmother'd come up with our tea. Be hadn't had to tell dad.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Were you allowed to get dirty when you played - get your clothes dirty?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Get our clothes dirty? We had to put on old clothes when we go out to play.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 She didn't mind if you got those dirty?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 No, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11162894\charrsid7682985 grandmother}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985  wouldn't let us have - have - what we go to school in put on. Change when we got home. And we always had 
a bath night - well, wash you know, for going to bed. Always had to kneel down and say our prayers before we got into bed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 She was very good wasn't }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11162894\charrsid7682985 she?}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Yes. She was - very strict on that. And grace at table, and our manners - we dare not - you 
know - say anything when we was having a meal. Get and eat up that food.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Were you allowed to talk at all at meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Well we did say some little thing, me grandmother'd say - you can't have a talk and eat your food up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Did you just have a wash in those days because you didn't have a bathroom did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5517773 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Did you ever have a bath in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10387110 PH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12791150\charrsid7682985 Yes. Yes, we had a tub. Down by the fire. Grandmother used to do always the washing Mondays.
